	<div id="content">
		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">List of best-selling books</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>This page provides lists of <b>best-selling single-volume books, book series, authors</b>, and <b>children's books</b> to date and in any language. For some books, accurate accounting has proven impossible, so the book is excluded or an educated guess by an expert is provided. "Best-selling" refers to the estimated number of copies sold of each book, rather than the number of books printed or currently owned. Comics and textbooks are not included in this list. Book versions of plays, like Shakespeare's works, are also excluded.</p>
<dl>
<dd>
<div class="boilerplate metadata plainlinks" id="listdev"><i>This is an <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Lists#Incomplete_lists" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Lists">incomplete list</a>, which may never be able to satisfy certain standards for completeness. You can help by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_best-selling_books&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_best-selling_books&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">expanding it</a> with <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Reliable_sources" title="Wikipedia:Reliable sources">sourced</a> additions.</i></div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:352px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Gutenberg_Bible.jpg" class="image" title="Gutenberg Bible, Library of Congress, Washington D.C."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Gutenberg_Bible.jpg/350px-Gutenberg_Bible.jpg" width="350" height="236" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Gutenberg_Bible.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<i>Gutenberg Bible</i>, <a href="/wiki/Library_of_Congress" title="Library of Congress">Library of Congress</a>, <a href="/wiki/Washington_D.C." title="Washington D.C." class="mw-redirect">Washington D.C.</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</dd>
</dl>
