<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_best-selling_books&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Claims of at least 1 billion copies">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Claims of at least 1 billion copies</span></h3>
