<td><i><a href="/wiki/Bible" title="Bible">Bible</a></i> <sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> (<a href="/wiki/Koine_Greek" title="Koine Greek">Koine Greek</a> <i>τὰ Βίβλια</i>)</td>
<td>Traditional Judaeo-Christian view: <a href="/wiki/Revelation" title="Revelation">Revelation</a> or Inspiration by <a href="/wiki/God" title="God">God</a><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup> to <a href="/wiki/Authors_of_the_Bible" title="Authors of the Bible">various authors</a></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Hebrew_language" title="Hebrew language">Hebrew</a>, <a href="/wiki/Koine_Greek" title="Koine Greek">Koine Greek</a>, <a href="/wiki/Aramaic_language" title="Aramaic language">Aramaic</a></td>
