<td>Quotations from <a href="/wiki/Mao_Zedong" title="Mao Zedong">Mao Zedong</a>; collected by the <a href="/wiki/PLA_Daily" title="PLA Daily">PLA Daily</a> of the <a href="/wiki/People%27s_Liberation_Army" title="People's Liberation Army">People's Liberation Army</a> and signed by <a href="/wiki/Lin_Biao" title="Lin Biao">Lin Biao</a></td>
